163
00:06:27,085 --> 00:06:28,553
O tak.

164
00:06:28,554 --> 00:06:33,791
[ziewa]

165
00:06:33,792 --> 00:06:36,561
Jak się masz, Michael?

166
00:06:36,562 --> 00:06:38,062
Dobrze.

